com.deltaxml.api

Interface ComparisonHeartbeatListener


  • public interface ComparisonHeartbeatListener
    A listener which receives events from the XMLComparator indicating that progress has been made in the current comparison. An event will be received at most once a second.

    Note: Not getting a response from this listener should not be interpreted as the comparison stopping or being broken, but usually a sign that the comparison is busy processing. Adding this will increase the comparison time by approximately 2.5%.

    Since:
    6.4
